<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

    <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Lego Collection</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/main.css" />

    </head>

    <body tabindex="-1">

    <%- include('partials/navbar',{page: ''}) %>

    <div class="container mx-auto p-4">


        <div class="hero bg-base-200 rounded-lg p-6">
        <div class="hero-content text-center ">
            <div class="max-w-md">
            <h1 class="text-5xl font-bold">Welcome</h1>

            <p class="py-6">Welcome to our Lego collection! Dive into the world of creativity and fun with our extensive
                selection of Lego sets.</p>
        
            <a href="/lego/sets" class="btn btn-primary">Get Started Now</a>
            </div>
        </div>
        </div>

        <br />

        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-4">
        <div>

            <div class="card bg-base-100 shadow-xl">
            <figure>
                <img class="w-full" src="https://cdn.rebrickable.com/media/sets/028-1.jpg" alt="Lego set" />
            </figure>
            <div class="card-body">
                <h2 class="card-title">Nursery Furniture</h2>
                <p>Released in 1979 with 7 parts, this set is a classic in the Playhouse theme.</p>
                <div class="card-actions justify-end">
                <a href="/lego/sets/001-1" class="btn btn-primary">View</a>
                </div>
            </div>

            </div>
        </div>
        <div>

            <div class="card bg-base-100 shadow-xl">
            <figure>
                <img class="w-full" src="https://cdn.rebrickable.com/media/sets/021-1.jpg" alt="Lego Set" />
            </figure>
            <div class="card-body">
                <h2 class="card-title">Wheel Set</h2>
                <p>A set from 1966 featuring 183 parts, part of the Basic Set theme.</p>
                <div class="card-actions justify-end">
                <a href="/lego/sets/0011-2" class="btn btn-primary">View</a>
                </div>
            </div>

            </div>
        </div>
        <div>

            <div class="card bg-base-100 shadow-xl">
            <figure>
                <img class="w-full" src="https://cdn.rebrickable.com/media/sets/02-1.jpg" alt="Lego Set" />
            </figure>
            <div class="card-body">
                <h2 class="card-title">Extra Large Tires & Hubs</h2>
                <p>Released in 1982 with 4 parts, another great addition to the Technic theme.</p>
                <div class="card-actions justify-end">
                <a href="/lego/sets/02-1" class="btn btn-primary">View</a>
                </div>
            </div>

            </div>
        </div>
        </div>
    </body>
    <!-- Footer -->
